subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Kasey Kahne’s victory at the Pocono 500 on Sunday was the second in three Nascar Sprint Cup races for the 28-year-old from Enumclaw, Wash.
